 {"id":"cass_memory_system-ck9","title":"[Playbook] getActiveBullets - Get non-deprecated bullets","description":"## Function Signature
```typescript
function getActiveBullets(playbook: Playbook): PlaybookBullet[]
```

## Purpose
Get all non-deprecated bullets from the playbook. Most common filtering operation for context generation.

## Implementation
```typescript
return playbook.bullets.filter(b => 
  b.state !== "retired" && 
  b.maturity !== "deprecated"
);
```

## Active vs Deprecated
**Active bullets**:
- state: "draft" or "active" (not "retired")
- maturity: "candidate", "established", or "proven" (not "deprecated")
- Used in agent context
- Subject to feedback and promotion

**Deprecated bullets**:
- state: "retired"
- maturity: "deprecated"
- Excluded from context
- Kept for historical record

## Usage Frequency
This is one of the MOST frequently called functions:
- Every context generation: getActiveBullets()
- Every markdown export: getActiveBullets()
- Every stats calculation: getActiveBullets()
- Every search: getActiveBullets()

## Performance Considerations
- Simple filter operation: O(n)
- Consider caching for repeated calls
- Most playbooks have < 100 bullets
- Filter is fast enough for real-time use

## Return Value
```typescript
PlaybookBullet[]  // Unsorted - caller should sort as needed
```

## Common Post-Processing
```typescript
// Sort by effective score
const active = getActiveBullets(playbook)
  .sort((a, b) => calculateEffectiveScore(b) - calculateEffectiveScore(a));

// Group by category
const byCategory = groupBy(getActiveBullets(playbook), "category");

// Top N rules
const topRules = getActiveBullets(playbook)
  .sort(byScore)
  .slice(0, 10);
```

## Dependencies
- None (pure function)

## Related Functions
- getBulletsByCategory() - filtered active bullets
- exportToMarkdown() - uses this for export
- generateContext() - uses this for LLM context
- calculatePlaybookStats() - uses this for metrics","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-07T16:45:12.297655-05:00","updated_at":"2025-12-07T20:07:53.562766-05:00","closed_at":"2025-12-07T20:07:09.578012-05:00"}
